title: PPPP Fayyaz Ali Butt wins PS-81 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarians’ (PPPP) Fayyaz Ali Butt has won the Sindh Assembly election from PS-22, Dadu-II by securing 54,338 votes.
According to unofficial result issued by Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Liaqat Ali Jotoi of , Grand Democratic Alliance,who bagged  votes 46,963.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 48.07 %.
